    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    EaseUS Data Recovery Wizard utilizes advanced data recovery algorithms that scan storage devices at the deepest level to locate and reconstruct lost files. When a file is deleted, the operating system typically only removes the file's reference (pointer) while the actual data remains on the drive until overwritten. The software works by bypassing the file system and reading raw data directly from the storage medium, identifying file signatures, and rebuilding the original files .
    
    🔹 RECOVERY PROCESS
    The program follows a sophisticated three-phase scanning approach:
    
    • QUICK SCAN: Rapidly scans the file system for recently deleted files by examining the Master File Table (MFT) and directory structures. This recovers files that were deleted but whose data hasn't been overwritten .
    
    • DEEP SCAN: Performs a comprehensive sector-by-sector analysis of the entire storage device, searching for file signatures (headers and footers) of known file types. This can recover files even after formatting, partition loss, or when the file system is damaged .
    
    • RAW RECOVERY: Advanced mode that recovers files based on their unique signatures without relying on file system information. Essential for severely corrupted drives or unrecognized partitions .
    
    🔹 SUPPORTED STORAGE DEVICES
    The software works with virtually any storage medium:
    
    • HARD DRIVES: Internal and external HDDs (SATA, IDE, SCSI, etc.)
    • SSDS: All solid-state drives including NVMe and M.2
    • USB DRIVES: Flash drives, thumb drives, pen drives
    • MEMORY CARDS: SD, microSD, CF, XD, MMC, Memory Stick
    • DIGITAL DEVICES: Cameras, camcorders, music players
    • OPTICAL MEDIA: CDs, DVDs, Blu-ray discs (non-scratched)
    • RAID ARRAYS: RAID 0, 1, 5, 10 (with proper configuration)
    • VIRTUAL DRIVES: VMware, VirtualBox, Hyper-V virtual disks
    
    🔹 FILE FORMAT SUPPORT
    Recovers 1000+ file types including:
    
    • DOCUMENTS: DOC/DOCX, XLS/XLSX, PPT/PPTX, PDF, TXT, RTF
    • IMAGES: JPG/JPEG, PNG, GIF, BMP, TIFF, RAW, CR2, NEF, ARW
    • VIDEOS: MP4, AVI, MOV, MKV, WMV, FLV, 3GP, MTS, MXF
    • AUDIO: MP3, WAV, WMA, AAC, FLAC, OGG, M4A
    • ARCHIVES: ZIP, RAR, 7Z, TAR, GZ, ISO
    • EMAILS: PST, OST, DBX, EML, MSG
    • DATABASES: MDB, ACCDB, SQL, MDF, NDF
    • CODE: HTML, CSS, JS, PHP, PY, JAVA, CPP, CS
    
